Welcome to my portfoli! I am a software developer, based in Milton Keynes.

About me

I am an apprentice software developer at a small company called Prominent Media. My primary focus is ASP.NET web applications, working with C# and MySql/SQL. From time to time, I explore the realms of Xamarin, and working with web sockets and APIs. Although, ASP.NET Core is my current obsession.
